  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UtvarAndIntervalBasedCrimeSummary, UtvarBasedCrimeSummary, java.io.Serializable

    public class CrimesSummary
extends CrimesSummaryBasic
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class used to provide the statistics for all crimes for a particular police department and crime data interval.

    All of the contained statistics relate to the given police department and the given crime data interval.

    The statistics provided are:

    • the crime index
    • the crime solved ratio
    • the crime trend
    • the logical chart of crime counts for each crime kind (TSK)

    The chart of crime counts for each crime kind is a series of CrimeSummary observations for each crime kind. Each observation includes the TSK identifier, the crime's name and the number of committed crimes of that kind.

    Author:
    Tom
